"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Hello ,everyone .Do you konw about the domians of celo chain? if not , that is ok,come with me and  reserve a nom domains for your ownself,now!\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/2R4lgrv71nfQ77QS8DtnM.jpg?height=297&width=491)\\n\\n## 1.Get CELO\\n\\nWe assume that you are experienced cryptocurrency investors, we will skip the part on how to use a centralized exchange.\\n\\n### （1）. Purchase CELO On Centralized Exchanges\\n\\n* You may purchase CELO on many centralized exchanges in the link below\\n\\n  （\\n\\n  <https://coinmarketcap.com/currencies/celo/markets/>\\n\\n  ）\\n\\n[https://coinmarketcap.com/currencies/celo/markets/](https://coinmarketcap.com/currencies/celo/markets/)\\n\\n* We recommend you to buy CELO on Binance: <https://www.binance.com/en/trade/CELO_BUSD>\\n\\n### （2）. Withdraw CELO To Your MetaMask\\n\\n* As CELO Network can be used on MetaMask wallet, you may withdraw CELO on Binance to your MetaMask wallet.\\n* Go to the withdrawal link: [https://www.binance.com/en/my/wallet/account/main/withdrawal/crypto/CELO](https://www.binance.com/en/my/wallet/account/main/withdrawal/crypto/CELO?)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/JtOQ2Zv3YHizADfadATjQ.png?height=902&width=960)\\n\\n* After successfully withdrawn CELO from Binance to your MetaMask, let's move on to the next step: **Configure Celo Network**.\\n\\n## 2. Configure Celo Network\\n\\nIn this part, we will give you 2 methods to configure Celo Network\\n\\n### （1）. Using Chainlist.org\\n\\n* Go to Chainlist — A tool helping users connect to EVM powered networks: [https://chainlist.org](https://chainlist.org/)\\n* Follow these steps:\\n\\n![(a) Input \\\"Celo\\\" in search bar; (b) Click \\\"Connect wallet\\\"](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/Kg9tsMKtWCg0pta2wqzKR.png?height=473&width=1000)\\n\\nChoose the wallet you would like to connect and click \\\"Next\\\". Then click \\\"Connect\\\"\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/bFjk7xCZsAzwI6Br3nBfZ.png?height=803&width=987)\\n\\n* After successfully connected, click \\\"Add To Metamask\\\"\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/GXCKim2fAF0WugZ5VLyLB.png?height=326&width=1056)\\n\\n* Click \\\"Approve\\\" and \\\"Switch network\\\". You're done!\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/6FGUsoaA25i0ciyZSJ7Pv.png?height=679&width=883)\\n\\nAnother Way is Configuring Directly On Your MetaMask\\n\\n* Open MetaMask, click your profile image on the top right corner, and then click \\\"Settings\\\".\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/WSbAbEdS0UKBvPjjPuHq7.png?height=752&width=447)\\n\\n* Next, scroll down and click to \\\"Networks\\\". Press the \\\"Add Network\\\" button.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/ndVxsAynrIPd2SSfC9vxv.png?height=778&width=953)\\n\\n* Fill out the following values of Celo Network:\\n\\n  **Network Name:** Celo Network\\n  **New RPC URL:** https://forno.celo.org\\n  **Chain ID:** 42220\\n  **Currency Symbol:** CELO\\n  **Block Explorer URL:** https://explorer.celo.org\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/cqIc3HVQ9pR3P8hYGDdpA.png?height=643&width=925)\\n\\n* Click \\\"Save\\\" and you will see CELO in your MetaMask wallet\\n\\n## 3. Go to the website: app.nom.space\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/r82GegrVoW1rcd4EXV-ha.png?height=942&width=1920)\\n\\nsearch the name what you like .If you have unique characters, spaces, and/or underscores those names will not be valid.a few emojis and the characters above the keyboard numbers like %^&\\\\*()!@#$.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/ASzawwmqg6QJXMiCxrsPI.png?height=942&width=1920)\\n\\nReserve it .\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/kRsiVKBaVceSd-zHRc2Uz.png?height=942&width=1920)\\n\\nwe can reserve it with cUSD\\n\\nIf you don’t have cUSD,you can exchange celo to cUSD in ubeswap(\\n\\n[https://app.ubeswap.org/#/swap](https://app.ubeswap.org/#/swap)\\n\\n)\\n\\n$5 cusd / year for the domians \\n\\nAfter you reserve the domians\\n\\nYou should go to change the resolution, all you have to do is to click on 'CHANGE' and copy-paste the alphanumeric address of your wallet. You must select the celo chain first!\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/XriJsIzbD5FyX673wPdSd.png?height=942&width=1920)\\n\\nNow,all step is done for reserve nom domains.\\n\\nBy the way , nom 2.0 is coming now!    UI will be updated.\\n\\nJust enjoy it!\\n\\nChinese version：\\n\\nhttps://mirror.xyz/hhhsssyyy.eth/P9vBBTH9OxKEGnz1l7qto9GNk_SroCFxWekGviLa3x0\",\"timestamp\":1641488338,\"title\":\"HOW TO GET A TOP DOMAINS OF CELO CHAIN                          \\n       --THE NOMSPACE DOMAINS\"},\"digest\":\"PqOkazmcPZwbGXjM9uHUOtggoxOQxpJ1bt8eP2cX2hU\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xC3Dcc314cc33F56ba4cAAD3d2885a5c23149923E\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"Gb__q0zonMz2mqXT9KxZ-QcSVyrSdSkaYba0YwYYElI\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"GeI981D_1cB7Qd48KJBs6_lE4Z1spy2YFby-JaOu4MI\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"A6U2qjbtPHv6LrF7tyQ15zQIQxvxtdVqVL4PwS_FmQI_RXQ7ih9aI00-HLRnHhoDcfeE9hKNjGBoYa0NbBCfog\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x8c5f1d8a55e4c76cb76b2e2e47d89da29e4c469ccc08a0093e4837fa7df737be172159ce11f13317991d62ce459d87db605bcf8e5d6ec8fa5093c7b2f8a18ad51b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"Gb__q0zonMz2mqXT9KxZ-QcSVyrSdSkaYba0YwYYElI\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"GeI981D_1cB7Qd48KJBs6_lE4Z1spy2YFby-JaOu4MI\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"8bGSkmwRkmMm8r_3xGWMGyEoWDW3odsVmVxKKM7Wakc\"}"